Description: At the bakery brought by TLC_s Cake Boss, you may have to stand in line, but a taste of his elegant cakes, lobster tail, and daily confections promise to be worth the wait.Opened in 1910, Carlo_s Bakery is renowned for its delicious creations, hardworking staff, and family atmosphere. Carlo_s has spearheaded the recent custom cake craze and has garnered attention from a variety of media outlets including Brides, The Rachael Ray Show, Huffington Post and Good Morning America. Most recently, Carlo_s has been showcased as the setting for TLC_s hit shows Cake Boss and Next Great Baker.
Location: 3355 S Las Vegas Blvd, Las Vegas, NV 89109

Description: Located poolside off The Venetian fourth floor, Canyon Ranch Caf‚ is the perfect place to detox with organic, non-GMO ingredients, from organic juices like the Vegas Recovery to grass-fed beef and wild salmon.No visit to Canyon Ranch spa + fitness _ or Las Vegas _ is complete without trying the world-famous cuisine of Canyon Ranch. Renowned chefs draw on the great culinary cultures of the world to create delicious, satisfying, made-from-scratch meals that you can feel good about enjoyingFeed your mind, body and spirit at Canyon Ranch Caf‚.  The nourishing qualities of ancient grains is reborn in this quick, delicious natural experience.  Our ingredients are organic whenever possible and always free of additives and preservatives. From organic vegetables to grass fed beef and troll caught wild salmon, you are given the tools to customize your own dining experience.

Description: When we put the words burgers, shakes and fries on the outside of our building it_s a commitment _ not only to you, but to ourselves to always strive to serve the absolute best.  How do we do it?  We start with the highest quality ingredients, including fresh never frozen 100% beef, thick-cut Applewood smoked bacon, real Wisconsin cheddar cheese, cage free chicken and premium ice cream and then hand craft them into goodness. We put so much love and passion into our craft, we are willing to put our signature on every plate that leaves our kitchen.
